### PORTY & KONFIGURACE

```yaml
# LONGIN CORE SERVICES (HlavnÃ­ stroj - Longin Master)
LONGIN_WEB_UI: 3000          # Frontend React aplikace
LONGIN_CORE_API: 3001        # Backend API
LONGIN_CORE_WEBSOCKET: 3002  # WebSocket server (real-time)

# INFRASTRUCTURE SERVICES
DOCKER_SOCKET: /var/run/docker.sock  # Docker daemon
TRAEFIK_DASHBOARD: 8080      # Reverse proxy admin
TRAEFIK_API: 8081            # Traefik API

# DATABÃZE & CACHE
POSTGRES_PRIMARY: 5432       # PostgreSQL master
POSTGRES_REPLICA: 5433       # PostgreSQL replica (optional)
REDIS_MASTER: 6379          # Redis master
REDIS_REPLICA: 6380         # Redis replica (optional)

# MONITORING & LOGGING
PROMETHEUS: 9090             # Metrics collector
PROMETHEUS_PUSHGATEWAY: 9091 # Metrics gateway
GRAFANA: 3003               # Visualization
ELASTICSEARCH: 9200         # Log storage
KIBANA: 5601                # Log UI
LOGSTASH: 5044              # Log pipeline

# DEPLOYED APPLICATIONS (DynamickÃ© porty)
APP_BASE_PORT: 4000         # StartovacÃ­ port pro aplikace
APP_PORT_RANGE: 4000-5000   # Rozsah portÅ¯ (max 100 aplikacÃ­)

# DOCKER SWARM (Multi-machine)
SWARM_MANAGER_PORT: 2377    # Swarm manager komunikace
SWARM_NODE_PORT: 7946       # Swarm node komunikace (TCP)
SWARM_NODE_UDP_PORT: 7946   # Swarm node komunikace (UDP)
SWARM_OVERLAY_VXLAN: 4789   # Overlay network
```

