### 1. LONGIN CORE (API Gateway & Orchestrator)

**Popis:** CentrÃ¡lnÃ­ orchestrator vÅ¡ech sluÅ¾eb, komunikace s Docker, API gateway.

**OdpovÄ›dnost:**
