  // data: {
  //   appId: "uuid",
  //   status: "running" | "stopped" | "restarting" | "error",
  //   metrics: { cpu: 45.2, memory: 512 },
  //   timestamp: "2025-03-20T14:22:30Z"
  // }
});
```

**Event: `container:metrics`**

PoslÃ­lÃ¡no kaÅ¾dÃ½ch 5 sekund.

```javascript
